{"id": 2973, "genre": 1000, "title": "生活中的哪些多重备份，现在已经是你的日常操作了？", "description": "小区门卡办两张的就是你吧，毕竟丢了一张还有一张。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 0, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190527160646Wt5wN6puVfS8BcLd.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5864, "title": "生活中的哪些多重备份，现在已经是你的日常操作了？", "content": "1", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345723, "content": "文档编辑时随手保存/设置隔几分钟自动保存", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161325eigMj57aqYTzJAfV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345728, "content": "电影资源只存云端不靠谱，移动硬盘里也要存一份", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162226Iwci1utMW9CzqTJS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345729, "content": "门锁不仅配钥匙，还设置指纹和密码", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162443xdHY1M04brSCwAD5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345730, "content": "从单反里导出照片，习惯用“复制”而不是“剪切”来“粘贴”", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162806TUZcD7FtVhfeQpdl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345731, "content": "定期把聊天记录下载到本地", "image": "img/option/option/201905271632216uUXSpvNgFwsZiA7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345732, "content": "跟不熟悉的人打电话谈事，通话要录个音", "image": "img/option/option/20190527163647gTCXOvxGDI3kcNYb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345733, "content": "重要的日程安排，日历/微信/便签等都要同时设置提醒", "image": "img/option/option/20190527163929o0OYrS1KnVWFQfHl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345734, "content": "避免公众号失联，关注作者的个人号", "image": "img/option/option/20190527164243DgkKMm70Zj2pwcrU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}